{"article_id":"wS0CT5YVsL2uuoc8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On Thursday , the US House wrapped up a marathon week of public hearings for its impeachment inquiry into President Donald Trump .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"With lawmakers headed home for Thanksgiving break ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"the question on everyone ' s minds is \" what comes next ? \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"In its rough form , what ' s next is that the House Intelligence Committee and Chair Adam Schiff","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"will compile and submit a report of its investigation to the House Judiciary Committee .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The Judiciary Committee hasn ' t had jurisdiction on the narrow Ukraine-focused impeachment investigation ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"but it ' s the body","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that will decide whether or not to draft articles of impeachment","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"- the \" charges \" against Trump .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"There are no more public hearings on the schedule for now .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Of course , this could change","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"if someone else with valuable testimony comes forward .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"But some Democrats don ' t want to wait long for a star witness like former National Security Adviser John Bolton","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"- who has said","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"he won ' t testify","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"unless compelled by a court .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"\" He blew our timeline up , \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Rep. Stephen Lynch","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"( D-MA ) ,","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"a member of the House Oversight Committee told recently ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that testimony from other sources about Bolton made it seem like he was opposed to Trump ' s objectives in Ukraine .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"\" When we looked at the evidence","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"we wanted from him ,","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"we had other sources .","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"... He can be prickly at times ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"and you ' re not sure what he ' s going to come out with . \"","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"An Intelligence Committee spokesperson declined to comment","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"on whether there would be additional hearings before or after the Thanksgiving holiday , or when Schiff would submit his report .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"For a while , the buzz around Capitol Hill has been that the Judiciary Committee could draft articles","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"to send to the full House before Christmas .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"Some House Democrats have said","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"they ' d like to vote on impeachment by the end of the year ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"but there ' s still no set timeline .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"On Thursday , the Washington Post reported","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Senate Republicans are in talks with senior White House officials","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to limit a Senate impeachment trial to two weeks ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and it ' s likely the earliest","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"a trial could come","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"is January .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"On Thursday , House Speaker Nancy Pelosi left the door open to the possibility of more testimony ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"but was careful not to put forth any deadlines .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" All of this is up to the committees of jurisdiction .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"They have the responsibility","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"and they see the flow of evidence in fact , \"","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"\" We aren ' t finished yet ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"the day is not over ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and you never know","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"what testimony of one person may lead to need for testimony of the other ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"as we saw with Ambassador Taylor at the beginning of last week","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"bringing forth Mr. Holmes today . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"An aide to a member on the Intelligence Committee told","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"while there ' s some talk at the staff level","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"of holding more sessions ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Democrats are feeling confident","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"they have enough information about Trump ' s efforts","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"to co-opt US foreign policy","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"and compel the Ukrainian president to open investigations","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"that would benefit him politically .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"The House comes back to Washington the week after Thanksgiving ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"when work will resume .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"\" Certainly there ' s more to investigate re :","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"[ Secretary of State Mike ] Pompeo , etc. , \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"the aide said ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"\" but for the case against the president at this point we have more than enough . \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Pelosi also repeated her invitation to President Trump","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"to appear before the committees under oath .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" We haven ' t made any decision ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"as I said to the president ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"if you have any information","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"that is exculpatory ,","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"please bring it forward ,","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"because it seems the facts are uncontested as to what happened , \"","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" If you have reason","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"to convince people","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that something was different","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"- under oath -","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"please let us know . \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"The spotlight is about to move to the House Judiciary Committee","depth":2},{"id":84,"text":"After the Thanksgiving break is done ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"the intense focus around impeachment will likely switch from the Intelligence Committee to the Judiciary Committee .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"While the Intelligence Committee","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"( along with the House Foreign Affairs and Oversight committees )","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"has had jurisdiction over the House ' s impeachment investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"the Judiciary Committee will ultimately be the group","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"deciding whether or not to move articles ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"which would then go to the Senate for the official trial","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"- if approved by the full House .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Here ' s how the rest of the House ' s side of the process works ,","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"as I wrote along with my colleagues Li Zhou and Matt Yglesias :","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Once House lawmakers ' investigation is complete","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"- we don ' t yet know","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"when that will be -","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"they can decide whether or not to recommend articles of impeachment , or charges","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"to be specifically brought against the president .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"The House Judiciary Committee would vote on these charges","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"and then advance them to a vote by the full House .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"The House then decides","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"if it officially wants to charge the president on these counts , a move","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"that requires a simple majority to pass .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Four Judiciary Committee members told on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"they ' re not yet sure the timeline will be .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"\" Judiciary won ' t do anything","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"[ on articles of impeachment ]","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"until the [ Intelligence ] Committee wraps up our work , \"","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"said Rep. Val Demings","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"( D-FL ) ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"who sits on both committees .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"When asked about the status of articles of impeachment in the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"committee member Ted Lieu","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"demurred .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"\" We haven ' t made a decision yet , \"","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Lieu said ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"he expected that to happen in December .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"\" There ' s still additional testimony .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"We also want to give every opportunity for the President to provide exonerating evidence . \"","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Another Judiciary Committee Democrat noted","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"it ' s significant that","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"despite Trump saying","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"he ' d \" strongly consider \" coming forward","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to testify ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"neither he or his White House has come forward to offer the exculpatory evidence","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"pushing back on the case","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"current and former intelligence and State Department officials have laid out around Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"\" I don ' t want to prejudge it ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"but this evidence is so damning ,","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"and you ' ll notice","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"there ' s no exculpatory information","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"coming out from the administration , \"","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"Rep. Madeleine Dean","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"( D-PA )","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"told .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"\" The picture is so abundantly painted clear now , \"","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"Dean added .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"\" The picture is clear for the American public . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":224,"right":282,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":171,"right":223,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":144,"right":170,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":0,"right":143,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":170,"left":150,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":145,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":6,"right":148,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":7,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":167,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":10,"right":166,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":151,"right":165,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":154,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":13,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":14,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"conditi